Ic̲h̲ësa guꞌn xnená lo nkëw, gol kwneꞌwu or xkëꞌ mbidz, gana diꞌltsa bekwaꞌn xnelanná lotá, gol kiep gik yu, gol kwneꞌwu ndip.
